room_title: Escape room "The Dig" by Escape the Room Chicago in Chicago
review: it was a great team building experience. We broke into teams and worked together to escape our rooms. It was fun to gather with coworkers outside of the office and do something so fun and laugh so hard.

room_title: Escape room "The Dig" by Escape the Room Chicago in Chicago
review: This was the first time we did an escape room.  We all had a blast even though we did not escape.  It was exciting to work through each section trying to figure out what to do next!

room_title: Escape room "The Dig" by Escape the Room Chicago in Chicago
review: Great fun for all the family! We had an amazing time. Great scenery and very clever clues. Wonderful entertainment and good for communication and relationship building.
